aln
TITLE prometheus-role-bands.v1.aln
VERSION 1.0.0
AUTHORITY ALN.MIGRATION.CYBERCOREAUTHORITY.v1
NAMESPACE Prometheus-Praxis
REPO mk-bluebird/Prometheus-Praxis

META
HOSTDID didalnorganic-host
PRIMARYBOSTROMADDRESS bostrom18sd2ujv24ual9c9pshtxys6j8knh6xaead9ye7
PROMETHEUSPRAXISREPO https://github.com/mk-bluebird/Prometheus-Praxis
DOCREF docs/prometheus-role-bands.md
ENDMETA

EPOCH
ROLEBANDSCHEMAVERSION 1
TRUSTSPECTRUM low,medium,high,sovereign
ENDEPOCH

SECTION ROLE-BANDS
ROW ROLEBAND DataIngestor
  TRUSTBAND low
  DESCRIPTION Writes raw telemetry to bounded data stores; no direct actuation.
  CAPABILITIES read:metrics,write:raw-store
  FORBIDDENCAPABILITIES write:actuators,modify:policy,spawn:agents

ROW ROLEBAND Validator
  TRUSTBAND medium
  DESCRIPTION Reads data and executes verification logic; no environment write.
  CAPABILITIES read:raw-store,read:agents,execute:verifiers
  FORBIDDENCAPABILITIES write:actuators,modify:policy

ROW ROLEBAND Coordinator
  TRUSTBAND high
  DESCRIPTION Plans multi-agent workflows; cannot bypass safety guards.
  CAPABILITIES read:metrics,read:agents,write:plans,invoke:guards
  FORBIDDENCAPABILITIES modify:global-envelopes,disable:guards

ROW ROLEBAND Guardian
  TRUSTBAND sovereign
  DESCRIPTION Enforces global envelopes and ALN policies; cannot be disabled.
  CAPABILITIES read:everything,write:actuators,modify:policy,halt:agents
  FORBIDDENCAPABILITIES self-downgrade,self-disable
ENDSECTION

SECTION LEDGER
ROW LEDGERKIND RoleBandAssignment

ROW FIELD assignment_id string!
ROW FIELD agent_id string!
ROW FIELD roleband string!
ROW FIELD trustband string!
ROW FIELD hostdid string!
ROW FIELD bostromaddress string!
ROW FIELD timestamputc RFC3339

ROW INVARIANT hostdid == HOSTDID
ROW INVARIANT bostromaddress == PRIMARYBOSTROMADDRESS
ROW INVARIANT roleband ∈ {DataIngestor,Validator,Coordinator,Guardian}
ENDLEDGER

SECTION BINDINGS
ROW BINDING RUSTMODULE
ROW TARGET crates/agent-registry/src/role_band.rs
ROW STRUCT RoleBand enum DataIngestor,Validator,Coordinator,Guardian
ROW FUNCTION parse_role_band,str -> RoleBand
ROW FUNCTION role_band_trust,RoleBand -> String
ROW PROOFMETHOD KANI
ROW PROOFFILES crates/agent-registry/tests/kani_role_band.rs
ENDBINDINGS

ENDSHARD
